title: Tin Tin Vegetarian Food - Gurney Plaza
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Chinese, International, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Malaysian
description: Vegetarian vendor in the G food hall in the basement of the mall. Menu includes soups, rice dishes, noodles and veggie versions of continental dishes including veggie fish and chips. Seating is shared with other vendors. Another branch in 1st Avenue Mall.
